	The conditions found at the time of inspection are not the typical conditions maintained at our estabishment. We pride ourselves in the high hygiene standards maintained thoughout the restaurant. A full investigation was carried out into the reasons behind the results of the inspection and subsequently one member of staff was dismissed with immediate effect. We will of course be applying for reinspections to attain a score we feel is more reflective of our business.&lt;/p&gt;
